CMS Compatibility Notice
=========================

Ikabud Kernel is designed to work with the following Content Management Systems:

- WordPress (https://wordpress.org/) - GPL v2 or later
- Joomla (https://www.joomla.org/) - GPL v2
- Drupal (https://www.drupal.org/) - GPL v2 or later

These CMS platforms are separate software projects with their own licenses.
Ikabud Kernel does not include or redistribute these CMS platforms. Users
must obtain and install them separately according to their respective licenses.

